      "created": "2014-09-12T19:56:58.563+0000",
      "description": "After YARN-2468, the container logs will be aggregated separately based on the time. It will increate the total number of log files. It is fine for small cluster. But for the larger cluster, it will make too-many-files problem even worse.\n\nWe need to find a more scalable way to handle those logs. Aggregate all container logs in a single file is an option, but we need to find a different way, other than TFile(do not support append), to do it.",
